[32m+[m[32m    Growth Tier (Intermediate):[m
[32m+[m[32m    â€¢ R2,240 - R17,920[m
[32m+[m[41m    [m
[32m+[m[32m    Premium Tier (Advanced):[m
[32m+[m[32m    â€¢ R35,840 - R50,000[m
